sequenceDiagram
    participant User as Data Scientist
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API Server<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant Webhook as kserve-webhook-server<br/>443/TCP HTTPS mTLS
    participant Controller as kserve-controller-manager<br/>ServiceAccount Bearer
    participant Init as storage-initializer<br/>Init Container
    participant S3 as S3/GCS Storage<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant Client as External Client
    participant Gateway as Istio IngressGateway<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant VirtualService as VirtualService<br/>Istio Routing
    participant Predictor as Predictor Pod<br/>8000/TCP HTTP/HTTPS
    participant Broker as Knative Eventing Broker<br/>8080/TCP HTTP

    Note over User,Controller: Flow 1: Model Deployment
    User->>K8sAPI: kubectl create InferenceService<br/>Bearer Token (OAuth)
    K8sAPI->>Webhook: POST /mutate-serving-kserve-io-v1beta1-inferenceservice<br/>mTLS (API Server client cert)
    Webhook-->>K8sAPI: Mutated InferenceService
    K8sAPI->>Webhook: POST /validate-serving-kserve-io-v1beta1-inferenceservice<br/>mTLS
    Webhook-->>K8sAPI: Validation Response
    K8sAPI-->>User: InferenceService Created

    Controller->>K8sAPI: Watch InferenceService<br/>Bearer Token (ServiceAccount)
    K8sAPI-->>Controller: InferenceService Event

    Controller->>K8sAPI: Create Knative Service / Deployment<br/>Bearer Token
    Controller->>K8sAPI: Create VirtualService / Route<br/>Bearer Token

    Note over Init,S3: Flow 2: Model Download
    Init->>S3: GET /bucket/model-artifacts<br/>AWS IAM/GCP SA/Azure credentials
    S3-->>Init: Model Files (TLS 1.2+)

    Note over Client,Predictor: Flow 3: Inference Request
    Client->>Gateway: POST /v1/models/mymodel:predict<br/>Bearer Token (optional)
    Gateway->>VirtualService: Forward (TLS 1.2+)
    VirtualService->>Predictor: HTTP/HTTPS Request<br/>mTLS (optional via Istio)<br/>Bearer Token (optional)
    Predictor->>Predictor: Run Inference
    Predictor-->>VirtualService: Prediction Result<br/>JSON Response
    VirtualService-->>Gateway: Response
    Gateway-->>Client: HTTPS Response

    Note over Predictor,Broker: Flow 4: Request Logging (Optional)
    Predictor->>Broker: Log Request/Response<br/>TLS via Istio (optional)
